adjectives.description: unfrequent (comparative more unfrequent, superlative most unfrequent)

entries.meaning: Not frequent; not common; not happening often; infrequent.

verbs.description: unfrequent (third-person singular simple present unfrequents, present participle unfrequenting, simple past and past participle unfrequented)
